$var reg 1 J can_sell $end
$var reg 1 K credit_load $end
$var reg 1 L clear $end
$var reg 1 M mem_write $end
$var reg 1 N sel_change $end
$var reg 1 O load_change $end
$var reg 1 P cancel_collect $end

$scope module u_fsm $end
$var wire 1 7 clk $end
$var wire 1 8 rst $end
$var wire 1 9 coin_in [1] $end
$var wire 1 : coin_in [0] $end
